item.title: Someone please help me fix this error!
item.dc:creator: @alexwright10 alexwright10
item.description:
@alexwright10 wrote:

Your using matrix or corrupted-souls, am i right?

It’s probably an anti-leach that the owner of the server has put there to stop you from leaching his source and using it as your own. If you can’t fix the anti-leach then you should probably stop with servers but they’re easy to fix, open bracket above Commands.java:2134 maybe, just look around commands.java until you find some sort of code that seems out of place or something that hasn’t been closed by a bracket.
